## Environment v0.1 Design

### Assets
- One tradable asset
- Initial cash: 10000
- Initial shares: 0
- Price series: fixed list, e.g. [10, 11, 12, 9, 13]

### Actions
- 0: Hold
- 1: Buy one share
- 2: Sell one share

### State
- cash
- shares
- current price
- day

### Reward
- reward = new portfolio value - previous portfolio value

### Done
- Episode ends when all prices are used
